INSERT INTO public."Reviews" (review_id, user_id, book_id, rating, review) VALUES (1300, 723, 453, 5, 'This amazingly talented author has done it again -hit it straight outta the park! Excellent, non-stop, edge of your seat action. This last book of the series brought it all together -potential readers absolutely must start from the first book - each of the preceding three have also been edge of your seat, majorly addictive novels and definitely will not disappoint (refer to my other reviews for this amazing, talented author).One of the things I most enjoyed was the author''s ability to  bring his characters to life -so much so in fact that I had no difficulty whatsoever "seeing" this book inside my head and because of that exceptional talent I found myself growing rather attached to  this brave, "little bit crazy", "just turned 14", warrior with an amazingly huge heart and let us not forget Decker -totally nuts - but what a soldier - brave, dedicated & an all around great guy.My recommendation, given without any hesitation whatsoever, is to buy this book and every other book in this series...never a dull moment and a definite must read!Hoping like heck the author reconsiders and finds a way to carry the series on to the next level-he''ll definitely have a loyal following if he does.  Regardless of what he''s said about this being the final book I''m going to keep watching with fingers crossed for another book in this absolutely fantastic series.');
